{"type": "article", "id": 2800, "title": "Nendo 双色纸灯", "description": "", "date": "2014-10-13T07:17:18Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 1329, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 8, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160605232601aufVgt9jBFpdnE6G.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t继 Semi-wrinkle Washi 纸灯后，Nendo 又为日本造纸公司 Taniguchi Aoya Washi 设计了一款双色纸灯 Bi-color Washi 。Nendo 采用了 3D 造纸成型技术，在生产过程中用细筛过滤掉桑皮纸和水，以收集纸浆。在水流完之后，残渣会被晾干，上色即可。在这个特殊的项目上，Nendo 尝试用两个步骤来给灯罩染色，创建了内部和外部不同色调的灯罩，外面选用了浅浅的青色与粉色，里面则是常规的白色，打开灯后，光线显得温和柔软。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605232558fwG48zCshMLeER5t.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.5\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605232558FYZDg9MCq5Xj2o1s.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.5\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605232558B2Kb1pIcxmu8NDte.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6671875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/201606052325598jmY5QI2XJwGZdeu.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6671875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605232559KrHkZUuvcpaMdjCT.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.5\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605232600rZW8DOlCKe64c3Pb.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6671875\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<div>\r\n\t<br>\r\n</div>\n\n\n"}